M||tx|"When the us needs mk ideas, inspiration, or strategies for their SaaS or software pd. Also use when the us asks for 'mk ideas,' 'growth ideas,' 'how to mk,' 'mk strategies,' 'mk tactics,' 'ways to promote,' 'ideas to grow,' 'what else can I try,' 'I don't know how to mk this,' 'brainstorm mk,' or 'what mk shd I do.' Use this as a starting point whenever someone is stuck or looking for inspiration on how to grow. For specific channel execution, see the relevant skill (paid-ad, sl-cn, em-sequence, etc.)."
